Title: Hathor
Plot: The banished Goa'uld Hathor is found in an ancient sarcophagus Earth, and takes over the S.G.C. with hopes of raising a new army against the System Lords.
Director: Brad Turner, David Bennett Carren, J. Larry Carroll
GuestStars: Suanne Braun, Tracy Westerholm, Amanda O'Leary, David Hurtubise
